lead_paragraph: Five of the six Ethiopian athletes suspended and under investigation for doping by the country's authorities tested positive for the newly banned substance meldonium, the national track team doctor said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Ethiopia Team Doctor to AP: 5 Athletes Failed for Meldonium
